# Testing and Debugging

> **Scope**: Manually attach when debugging issues

## Enable Logging

| Platform | Command |
|----------|---------|
| macOS | `RUST_LOG=debug ./clean_run.sh` |
| Windows (PowerShell) | `$env:RUST_LOG="debug"; ./clean_run_windows.bat` |
| Audio-specific | `RUST_LOG=app_lib::audio=debug ./clean_run.sh` |

## Developer Tools

- Open DevTools: `Cmd+Shift+I` (macOS) / `Ctrl+Shift+I` (Windows)
- Console Toggle: Built into app UI

## Audio Metrics

- Buffer sizes (mic/system)
- Mixing window count
- VAD detection rate
- Dropped chunk warnings

## Platform Quirks

| Platform | Key Issue |
|----------|-----------|
| macOS | ScreenCaptureKit needs macOS 13+ + screen recording permission |
| Windows | WASAPI exclusive mode can conflict with other apps |
| Linux | Needs cmake, llvm, libomp |